USB STICK README

Distributions of agilesms do not require installation of 
dependency or installation at all. They can be run from a stick.

USING:

Download agilesms.zip from GitHub, unzip onto USB stick
Plug in USB stick, click on mac/ or windows/ depending on your system.

INSTALL SMS DRIVERS FIRST. You'll have a CD or they will install from the web when 
you plug in the device. agilesms does not provide drivers yet

WINDOWS:
Double-click on agilesms.exe

MAC:
Double-click on agilesms.command
